{"tid":210384,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[少女藏刀]遭色阿伯強拉摸下體　國中妹淚訴：要帶美工刀才敢外出","createTime":"2017-04-21T01:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T06:36:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df5caa0c1e67b47cd3ee0edb1c08298ed7cd14da","tid":210384,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>遭色阿伯強拉摸下體　國中妹淚訴：要帶美工刀才敢外出</strong><br />\n<br />\n新北市60歲的林姓阿伯今年2月騎機車路過三重一棟公寓附近，發現一名落單的國中女學生長相清秀可愛，於是將人拐進樓梯間強摸下體。女學生掙脫後趕忙衝回家向媽媽哭訴，至今如果沒有帶美工刀防身就不敢獨自外出。<br />\n<br />\n受害女學生今年2月19日中午獨自走在路邊，當時騎機車經過的林男突然上前攀談，她見對方歲數與自己的爺爺差不多好心回應，沒想到才剛卸下心防就被強拉至一旁的公寓樓梯間，對方先是強行熊抱再拉下褲子拉鍊露出生殖器，還強拉她的手撫摸下體。<br />\n<br />\n接著，女學生驚覺林男伸手撫摸自己的私處，嚇得大喊「不要」並趕緊逃離，回家後哭著向母親訴說事情經過，還要求買美工刀防身，隔天甚至不敢獨自去上學，事發至今雖然已經經過2個月，但如果沒帶物品防身仍不敢獨自外出，心理嚴重受創。<br />\n<br />\n林男被逮後坦言，當時自己酒後「一時性起」，確實有強拉女學生撫摸下體並拉扯對方內褲，但聽到她喊不要就立即收手。新北地檢署昨日（20日）依強制猥褻罪將林男起訴，考量到受害少女仍未成年且心理創傷很深，於是再建請法院加重其刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/08/66/37/086637a6a1e1d8d83d78deb50fa51bbe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F08%2F66%2F37%2F086637a6a1e1d8d83d78deb50fa51bbe.gif&h=51efbada&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"311b1fbf12d8b0750e85d0ee87d07b8661c48d1a","tid":210384,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cbea8deec5778d0deabe60562ddb96315fbad31","tid":210384,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯"},{"pid":"75a2086a6b8d2bcc2cb3d713e4e22ca2d55d4c6f","tid":210384,"uid":86946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"921e4c2ac41792eeb7dd01e71e28eea56c66d022","tid":210384,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n+2"},{"pid":"3ef152054370b80e77dc13580b7d519e1902fe8f","tid":210384,"uid":67261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n唔係你講睇錯阿拉伯   我仲以為緊真係阿拉伯<br />\n心諗又台灣又阿拉伯咁 啫係點"},{"pid":"9e374def5e94a6149826a5fb2b0294bde0436c26","tid":210384,"uid":80777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n+2</blockquote><br />\n+3"},{"pid":"cfc2e7335171fdd52809a49a672027548c3b2adc","tid":210384,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇錯中國妹</blockquote><br />\n睇錯阿拉伯</blockquote><br />\n+1</blockquote><br />\n+2</blockquote><br />\n+3</blockquote><br />\n+4"},{"pid":"3733d5517e01ee1a3582ca21981164df9ecd6480","tid":210384,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9508e50a8decb9744314abbd6cf5b4d7c85ec456","tid":210384,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"阿拉伯色魔強行摸中國少女下體<br />\n<br />\n第一眼睇成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}